com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.security

Class SCUIAuthenticationProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.security.SCUIAuthenticationProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISCUIAuthenticationProvider, ISCUISessionAware, ISCUISessionUserChangeAware

    public class SCUIAuthenticationProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISCUIAuthenticationProvider
    SCUIAuthenticationProvider is the implementation class for ISCUIAuthenticationProvider. It turns around and calls YFSUILoginManager#Login(HttpServletRequest, HttpServletResponse).
    If the userId is null in the request parameter it uses guest login if given as context parameter. If the guest login is not given in the context parameter, the login will automatically fail. rasrinivasan
